We exemplify our analytical framework with the dataset originally used by Diniz‐Filho et al. (
 2009). This dataset includes the extents of occurrence (range filling) for 1,205 Neotropical bird species. The data were downloaded from the BirdLife (former Nature Serve; 
 http://www.datazone.birdlife.org) and resampled to a grid of 1° latitude × 1° longitude.
